    {
      "id": "standard_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_2",
      "description": "2019 Honda Accord EX-L in good condition. The engine and mechanical systems are functioning well with no significant issues. The interior shows minor wear consistent with normal use but is generally clean and presentable. The exterior has a few small scratches or blemishes but no major damage. Overall a reliable, well-maintained vehicle.",
