    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Wow, are you ready to fall in love? This vehicle is in absolutely mint condition \u2014 we're talking a flawless interior, a spotless exterior, and mechanical systems that are running perfectly. Every detail has been meticulously maintained, and it truly shows from the moment you lay eyes on it. If you've been searching for a car that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is your chance \u2014 don't let it slip away!",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
